  "detailed_description": "It is a game that collects materials, makes goods, sells money, and repairs a time machine.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFirst collect resources such as iron, wood, and stone. It can be made into swords, shields, arrows, etc., or you can add them to the defense of the castle.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you have enough money, you can hire someone to help you. They will gather resources like you, or make something. Even sales and delivery!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTime to spare time machine is completely repaired and return to the future will win!",
